articles.title: Here’s who will be on the ballot for November’s 2025 City Council election
articles.description:
The preliminary election narrowed down candidates before the general election Nov. 4.

The post Here’s who will be on the ballot for November’s 2025 City Council election appeared first on Boston.com.
summary: Preliminary election results determine candidates for Boston's City Council election on November 4, 2025.
Several candidates have emerged, setting the stage for a competitive general election.
Boston residents will vote on key local issues affecting their communities in the upcoming election.
